Oh, dear.

23:45.032 --> 23:47.338
Do you, uh,
do you like to swim?

23:47.513 --> 23:49.166
Uh, I don't have
a bathing suit.

23:49.297 --> 23:50.820
Oh.

23:50.951 --> 23:53.257
That is not going
to be a problem.

23:53.388 --> 23:54.955
Okay, for you
