32:15.020 --> 32:15.934
Good luck.

32:16.108 --> 32:17.457
Good luck!

32:19.372 --> 32:21.156
[sighs]

32:24.899 --> 32:26.553
Here you go, sir.

32:26.727 --> 32:28.250
Chopped salad, dressing

32:28.424 --> 32:29.817
on the side,
no onions.

32:29.991 --> 32:31.166
Thanks.

32:31.340 --> 32:33.690
And this was taped to your door.

32:49.793 --> 32:51.795
♪

32:53.362 --> 32:55.495
JIMMY:
They're gonna search
my house, Kenneth!

32:55.669 --> 32:56.626
There's got to be
something you can do!

32:56.800 --> 32:58.715
Come on!

32:58.889 --> 33:01.240
This isn't like getting
a small charge dropped, Jimmy.

33:01.370 --> 33:02.893
This is a federal issue
we're talking about.

33:03.068 --> 33:04.808
Y-You've got to have
a contact at the IRS.

33:04.983 --> 33:06.941
I don't.

33:07.115 --> 33:09.204
I prosecute local cases.
This is federal.

33:11.163 --> 33:12.512
These aren't like
the other times.

33:12.686 --> 33:14.253
What am I supposed to do
with all these pills I got?

33:14.383 --> 33:16.820
I don't know,
but I'd get rid of them. Fast.

33:16.995 --> 33:18.648
[scoffs]

33:20.650 --> 33:23.436
AUTOMATED VOICE:
Call from 847-55...

33:24.176 --> 33:26.091
[whispers]:
Who is it?Hello?

33:26.265 --> 33:27.744
Hey.

33:27.918 --> 33:29.877
It's Jimmy... McKay,
Jimmy McKay.

33:30.051 --> 33:31.966
We met last night.MURPHY: Oh, hi, Jimmy.

33:32.097 --> 33:33.315
Hi.

33:33.489 --> 33:35.448
You'd like to do a deal.Yes.

33:35.622 --> 33:37.189
JIMMY:
I would.
Yes.

33:37.363 --> 33:38.755
Um, that's great.
Well, why don't you...

33:38.886 --> 33:40.757
tell me when
to come over.

33:40.931 --> 33:42.672
Yeah, it doesn't
work like that.

33:43.760 --> 33:45.806
How does it work?

33:47.416 --> 33:49.462
Okay.

33:50.854 --> 33:52.682
So he has
this charity event tomorrow.

33:52.856 --> 33:55.076
It's like an exclusive dinner,
uh, at one

33:55.250 --> 33:57.644
of his hotels.
Uh, Darnell, my...

33:57.774 --> 33:59.428
lovely boyfriend,

33:59.559 --> 34:01.213
is going to be making

34:01.387 --> 34:03.215
a $500,000 donation,
because, apparently,

34:03.345 --> 34:05.130
that's how Jimmy launders
the money.

34:05.304 --> 34:06.609
Then the two of us...

34:06.783 --> 34:08.959
uh, boyfriend and I,

34:09.134 --> 34:11.310
we're gonna go
down to his room,

34:11.440 --> 34:14.008
and McKay's gonna be waiting
there with all of the pills.

34:14.139 --> 34:15.923
So we got to keep up

34:16.097 --> 34:17.794
this ruse we're a couple?

34:17.925 --> 34:19.883
Yeah.

34:20.014 --> 34:21.494
I mean,
I always thought we'd end up

34:21.668 --> 34:23.800
together. Stupid Max got
in the way, so...[chuckles]

34:23.974 --> 34:26.020
[chuckles]DARNELL:
Damn it, Max.

34:26.194 --> 34:28.457
Yeah, well, you can't see
how beautiful I am.

34:28.631 --> 34:30.459
That's true.

34:30.590 --> 34:31.678
GENE: I can't believe you
morons actually pulled this off.

34:31.852 --> 34:33.549
[laughter]

34:33.723 --> 34:35.812
Darnell will make sure
that Trey is at one of his labs,

34:35.986 --> 34:37.379
and we'll make
the arrest at the same time

34:37.553 --> 34:38.946
the McKay deal's
going down.

34:39.120 --> 34:39.729
That way they can't
warn one another.

34:39.903 --> 34:41.122
And then, poof...

34:41.296 --> 34:42.906
Murphy's free.

34:43.864 --> 34:45.257
Bolt is done.

34:45.431 --> 34:47.607
Okay.

34:47.781 --> 34:49.609
See you guys tomorrow?

34:49.783 --> 34:51.306
Yeah. See you tomorrow.

34:52.568 --> 34:53.656
It's fancy.[clears throat]

34:53.830 --> 34:55.180
I got it.

34:59.140 --> 35:01.186
♪

35:05.799 --> 35:07.540
[alarm chirping]

35:20.901 --> 35:22.294
Wake up.

35:22.424 --> 35:24.209
No.[chuckles softly]

35:25.645 --> 35:27.473
Mm.
Come on.

35:29.127 --> 35:31.129
Mm, no!

35:31.303 --> 35:32.652
[smooching]

35:32.826 --> 35:34.654
We got to get up.

35:34.828 --> 35:35.655
Got to go.

35:35.785 --> 35:37.091
Mm-hmm.

35:37.222 --> 35:39.876
I'm gonna hop
in the shower real fast.

35:40.007 --> 35:41.748
Fine, I'll join you.

35:41.922 --> 35:43.576
[laughs] Okay.

35:43.750 --> 35:44.794
Then hurry.

35:44.968 --> 35:47.145
Okay.
Let's go.

35:54.761 --> 35:57.459
[faucet squeaks, water running]

35:57.633 --> 35:59.200
[chuckles softly]

36:02.595 --> 36:05.119
When did you learn
how to do that?

36:05.293 --> 36:07.600
You'd be surprised how much
you can do without looking.

36:07.774 --> 36:10.080
[laughs]

36:10.255 --> 36:12.474
Should I see what Felix got
for us to wear to this thing?

36:12.648 --> 36:14.389
Oh, God. Can't wait.

36:16.696 --> 36:18.480
[sniffles]

36:35.671 --> 36:37.891
You know...

36:38.065 --> 36:40.067
I know how much you
hate dressing up.

36:41.416 --> 36:43.636
What do you mean? I love it.

36:43.810 --> 36:45.855
[chuckles]Here.

36:46.029 --> 36:47.509
Well, this feels expensive.

36:47.683 --> 36:49.294
And we sort of have
an event coming up

36:49.468 --> 36:51.687
that might require me
to be in a tux and...

36:51.861 --> 36:53.733
you in a dress.

36:55.604 --> 36:57.432
I can get married
in my hoodie if I want to.

36:57.606 --> 36:59.391
I know.

37:00.740 --> 37:02.611
Or...

37:02.742 --> 37:04.744
what if you only had
to get dressed up once?

37:06.963 --> 37:08.313
What do you mean?

37:08.487 --> 37:09.923
I mean, we wrap
this whole thing up,

37:10.097 --> 37:11.751
and we go get married.

37:13.492 --> 37:15.450
Like, tonight?Yeah, tonight.

37:15.624 --> 37:17.191
Like, this soon?

37:17.365 --> 37:18.540
I don't want to
wake up another day

37:18.714 --> 37:19.889
and not be
your husband.

37:20.063 --> 37:21.761
You're kidding me.

37:22.979 --> 37:24.720
[chuckling]

37:24.894 --> 37:25.678
[inhales]

37:25.852 --> 37:27.680
[sighs, snorts]

37:27.854 --> 37:29.551
Well...

37:29.725 --> 37:32.554
where are we gonna live,
husband of mine?

37:32.728 --> 37:34.426
As soon as I scrape
together some money,

37:34.556 --> 37:36.428
I'm gonna get us
a little house.

37:36.602 --> 37:39.169
Okay, well, I'm gonna scrape
together some money, too.

37:39.344 --> 37:40.823
What kind of house
do you see us in?

37:40.997 --> 37:43.348
Nothing fancy, just...

37:43.522 --> 37:44.653
a bed.

37:44.784 --> 37:46.220
Good.

37:46.394 --> 37:48.657
A little kitchen, so I can cook.

37:48.831 --> 37:50.790
And a patch of grass big enough
for a lemon tree.

37:52.008 --> 37:53.575
A lemon tree?Yeah.

37:53.749 --> 37:55.534
I know it's dumb,
but growing up we had

37:55.708 --> 37:57.362
this lemon tree.

37:57.536 --> 37:58.711
And my mom, she always used
to make us lemonade.

37:58.885 --> 38:00.887
It's, like...

38:01.017 --> 38:03.019
the one nice memory
I have of her.

38:03.150 --> 38:04.934
So...

38:05.108 --> 38:06.806
I always wanted a lemon tree.

38:06.980 --> 38:10.113
♪ Birds all sing... ♪

38:10.244 --> 38:12.290
Then let's get you a lemon tree.

38:12.464 --> 38:14.814
I thought you were gonna
make fun of me.

38:14.988 --> 38:17.033
You thought I was gonna make fun
of the one good memory

38:17.207 --> 38:19.166
you have of your dead mother?

38:19.340 --> 38:21.124
Who do you think I am?

38:21.255 --> 38:22.952
♪ And we'll never be lonely... ♪

38:23.126 --> 38:25.041
Um, this dress, this dress

38:25.172 --> 38:26.347
isn't white,is it?

38:26.521 --> 38:27.827
No.

38:28.001 --> 38:29.568
I never pictured myself

38:29.742 --> 38:31.221
doing the whole...

38:31.396 --> 38:32.571
white dress thing.Oh, come here.

38:32.745 --> 38:34.137
Come here.

38:34.268 --> 38:37.837
♪ Gonna get married ♪

38:38.011 --> 38:40.143
♪ Going to the chapel... ♪

38:40.318 --> 38:42.015
[grunting]

38:42.189 --> 38:43.756
♪ Gonna get married... ♪

38:43.930 --> 38:45.932
I still have
to finish my makeup.

38:46.106 --> 38:48.282
Fine.

38:48.456 --> 38:50.545
Fine, I'll wait
until marriage.

38:50.719 --> 38:52.895
Like a good
Christian boy.[chuckles]

38:53.069 --> 38:55.420
Okay, fine.

38:55.594 --> 38:57.509
Yeah, I guess I better
get dressed too, huh?

38:57.639 --> 39:00.294
♪ He'll be mine ♪

39:00.425 --> 39:02.731
♪ We'll love until... ♪

39:02.862 --> 39:04.298
[Murphy sobbing]

39:04.429 --> 39:05.952
MURPHY:
No!

39:06.126 --> 39:08.128
No, please...

39:08.302 --> 39:10.217
No!

